import React from 'react'

const MapSection = () => {
  return (
    <iframe
    className="google-map"
    title="google-map"
    src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m12!1m3!1d50476.4196895775!2d-75.5797569195202!3d6.248278886936033!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!5e0!3m2!1ssv!2sco!4v1667687577030!5m2!1ssv!2sco"
    allowFullScreen 
    loading="lazy" 
    referrerPolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade">

    </iframe>
  )
}

export default MapSection
